;; Usage: 
;;    r6rsmake.ss file.sls [purge]
;;      Rebuild file.sls and all dependencies.
;;
;;    r6rsmake.ss file.sls purge
;;      The optional "purge" argument will destroy dirty objects rather than rebuilding.
;;
;;    r6rsmake.ss file.sls list   
;;      List files that would be rebuilt.

